<br>
Congratulations, you're completely nuts.<br>
<br>
Smoothing out hell levels does NOTHING to speed up 1-50.  All they're doing is taking the &quot;extra&quot; exp that hell levels currently require and &quot;spreading it out&quot; over the non-hell levels.  It'll still take the same total exp to get there.<br>
<br>
And if you think that not having to chase down your corpse a few times from 1-10 is going to CUT IN HALF the amount of time it takes you to get from 1-50, well, I've got a bridge in the Karanas I'd like to sell you.<br>
<br>
For pete's sake, people, get a grip.<br>
<br>
Mostly Verant is removing the most aggravating parts without making it any &quot;easier&quot;, per se.  You're still going to have to kill tens of thousands of mobs to crank from 1-50, that will change very little.  They're just easing some of the more needlessly painful aspects of the journey.<br>
<br>
Will you be able to PL a twink pretty rapidly from 1-50?  Sure, but then you could *always* do that.  And your second character, even if untwinked (yeah, right!) also benefits from the fact that you know a hell of a lot more about the game now than you did when you first worked your main from 1-50.<br>
<br>
None of the proposed changes make any substantial difference in how long it takes to slog an untwinked character from 1-50, *or* how long it takes to PL a twink up to 50.<br>
<br>
So relax and unwind.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/upooh123.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Pooh123</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/16/02 9:02:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14852.topic&index=26>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Is the -50 game now pretty much trivial?</span><hr size=1> The road from 1-50 the first time is tough.  The second/thrid...it is just a matter of finding a spot that you can mow down unlimited mobs for max exp.<br>
<br>
Leveling to 50 pre RoK was MUCH MUCH MUCH harder then after, p leveled or not.  There simply was not enough mobs to go around.  There was no loio, dl, ot etc.  At 40+ you had L Guk, where all the pallys hung out and you had Solb.  These places were mega camped and you had very few mobs you could kill per hour.<br>
<br>
Remember, the 40% exp penalty we had?  That is like having to get 2 extra YELLOW bubs each level to level, compared to now.  That sucked.  Try level 35/40/45 with that going against ya and killing 10 mobs in an hour with a full group and no group exp modifier like now.  On top of that everyone had complete crap equipment and killing was just took sooo long.<br>
<br>
I'm not saying it was fun before RoK, just that it made you appreciate things more. I think people missed out on a lot of dungeon killing and earning of equipment.  <br>
