<br>
Both can be fun i think it's just about what you want to do and what's more fun for you.  I see it as compared to a lot of other computer or video games.  We all know about back in the day with the Game Geniie and things like that <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   I look at pling just like the cheat codes in other games.  It can be fun to be on god mode back in Doom (hehe that was a long time ago huh? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  )  but the novelty wears off i think after a while.  What fun is it to breeze through the lvls that way?  Some people enjoy it some people dont.  I usually dont.  <br>
